/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FnoTVBteam&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=0d9a0f28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/noTVBteam</a><br />\n<strong>隨時</strong> - <ins>美國聯署人權民主法案</ins> - <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XOf0aj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XOf0aj&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=bf87fe9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XOf0aj</a><br />\n</span><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>撤回修例 收回暴動 撤銷控罪 追究警隊 雙真普選<br />\n不割蓆，不篤灰，不分化</em></span></div>"},{"pid":"d6a4b75dd9c11307b8057e2473da69f103cb899c","tid":1301503,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:04:20.000Z","msg":"只要民選到特首同立法會就可以達成其他n大訴求"},{"pid":"5e29620f4d8ecd0d5564f1c0dc6a2518ed653fbb","tid":1301503,"uid":157762,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"如果唔轉化佢地 我地打持久戰嘅時候 會有一部份人覺得我地唔知足 諸如此類 所以轉化佢地嘅思想好重要"},{"pid":"7b8e2bc4037c83581876b853f13db2f26e57fddd","tid":1301503,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa25efbbca05775084b73cce4dd54eb19e716c46","tid":1301503,"uid":69891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"Yes 機會一過即逝"},{"pid":"c7ae2a15ac0ca8f2ee4f1cbb2d423751b1c0d1dd","tid":1301503,"uid":157762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:07:10.000Z","msg":"具體上可以咁講 如果有雙普選 根本唔會有送中惡法 又或者可以簡單d話 點解你有交稅 但係冇得話事"},{"pid":"76d5e7609ec7d0e56c79c462bdb64a81ca17fe16","tid":1301503,"uid":157762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:08:03.000Z","msg":"其實撤唔撤回可以慢慢淡出 重點係主權在民嘅意識"},{"pid":"5c38cf1d9162c61d94f4a677f71277f189bc5ca9","tid":1301503,"uid":157762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"07f6a38def63db55c7c6d5fabfb69240d1c59409","tid":1301503,"uid":157762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"同埋建立主權在民嘅意識係同時為2047做準備"},{"pid":"0ac9da3ade3b0f7ec88321311424f7a166285705","tid":1301503,"uid":58803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"覺，香港人無真普選先係問題根源<br />\n之前有部份人覺得突然講普選會令呢場運動失焦，我覺得而家可以將重心放多d 落雙普選度。<br />\n<br />\n還我真普選！還我真普選！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c762f6724d533af96de0b4ddbba832bdc5c1c301","tid":1301503,"uid":157762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:15:10.000Z","msg":"推到文宣組見到"},{"pid":"30304d49070592e9c55f68f92cb11711833cbffc","tid":1301503,"uid":260806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:57:54.000Z","msg":"我有稍微不同嘅意見<br />\n民主制度有三個最緊要嘅點：<br />\n1. 意見獲得充分表達（香港係投訴之都，表達能力冇問題）<br />\n2. 決策機制（俗稱少數服從多數，目前係冇嘅，立法會係少數騎劫多數）<br />\n3. 邊個係選民（呢個就係論述嘅關鍵）<br />\n<br />\n邊個係選民決定好多嘢，細緻來講，包括區議會選區劃分，到底要分幾多區，每區有幾多人。最大來講，就係香港必須<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">劃定邊界</span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明定公民身份</span></strong>。呢個邊界唔係物理上嘅疆界，而係政治上法理上何謂香港人嘅界線。<br />\n<br />\n無法劃定界線，任由外人侵入，有咩民主決策機制都冇用。爭取有合理嘅民主制度，實質就係香港成爲一個自主嘅政治實體，由具有呢種選舉權利嘅人組成。"},{"pid":"7f0eb64b545355be61fe9f2c79f8086a4ab4a698","tid":1301503,"uid":260806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:00:15.000Z","msg":"運動嘅最終目的，並非具體某個政客集團藉住運動而取得政治利益。而係香港人身份嘅最終覺醒。同《進擊的巨人》一樣，係一場<span style=\"color: red;\">身份覺醒</span>嘅運動。呢樣意味住乜嘢，大家都心照，唔需要點破。"},{"pid":"95fd05299e48121f8af7f92204faa91d932d5cfc","tid":1301503,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:01:13.000Z","msg":"轉文宣做雙普選之前要俾多D人知社會信用體系呢樣野<br />\n越多人知就推雙普選出去<br />\n<br />\n 【文宣】社會信用系統文宣圖，麻煩各位手足返工返學掟撚哂出去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301880</a>"},{"pid":"79abaf2f0a35de2d8fe90a7f3176e2f845680b68","tid":1301503,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}